{
  "stem": "868.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was advised by [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the archbishop that things were getting very tough in-- in-- in Florence.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had their informers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they knew that the Germans had their eye on him, Don Giovanni.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Mind you, he was all of maybe 25 years old at-- at the time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he was in Florence, because he was studying at the University there in addition of being chaplain at the convent.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was studying philosophy, history, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But that was not his birthplace.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "His birthplace was in the north of Italy, a town called Treviso, north of Venice.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But he found himself in Florence during these events.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But he kept taking care of all the Jews that he had been entrusted with, who before had been handled by Don Casini.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when the situation got worse-- because the German raids continued, not just for that one massive one that blanketed all of Florence.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They went on continuously on a lesser scale.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He decided his Jewish women are not safe enough.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What if they invade the convent itself, which they did?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In other convents people had been caught, the nuns taken prisoners, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He hit upon a radical solution.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the garden, behind the convent, there was an underground cave where they kept various gardening tools, and plants, and seeds, and bags of fertilizer, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All of this was removed, cleaned away, straw was brought in, and 12 women and children, girls, were brought to live in that cave.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The entrance was hidden by flower pots and so forth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Twice a day, a nun came with a special signal on the door.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The flower pots were removed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She brought in some soup, some food, and removed the urine pot.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
